  "lean_declaration": "/-- The `x^n`-coefficient in the sum of `(a_i)_{i ∈ I}` is finitely determined\nif there exists a finite subset `M` that determines it.\n(Label: def.fps.xn-coeff-fin-determined part (a)) -/\ndef CoeffFinitelyDeterminedInSum (a : I → PowerSeries R) (n : ℕ) : Prop :=\n  ∃ M : Finset I, DeterminesCoeffInSum a M n",
  "declaration_name": "CoeffFinitelyDeterminedInSum",
  "used_context": [
    "DeterminesCoeffInSum"
  ],
  "notes": [
    "This defines part (a) of def.fps.xn-coeff-fin-determined, which was missing from the Lean prefix context. The companion definition CoeffFinitelyDeterminedInProd is already present."
  ]
}
